I"ˆK<p>What we usually mean when talking about productivity is that we want to do what we need to do in the shortest possible time; that means keyboard shortcuts, templates, snippets etc. In this section, we‚Äôll take a peek at some of what Android Studio has to offer give our productivity a little boost. We won‚Äôt go into detail; that‚Äôs not the goal, but rather just to show you what‚Äôs available in Android Studio.</p>

